      <hedline>
        <hl1>Quest for Free Energy</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Carsten Saager comments on recent letter on quest for free energy</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The idea of capturing energy by having cars depress plates on the road, as suggested by a recent letter writer, would not work. But if someone could develop a technique to reuse the kinetic energy that is lost when a car stops at a light, that would be a different story.</p>
        <p>CARSTEN SAAGER  New York</p>
      </block>
